01:36:28,213 --> 01:36:31,973
How did you know I was here?
- My heart told me.

980
01:36:34,872 --> 01:36:36,394
You are Chandalika
in Rama's college...

981
01:36:36,627 --> 01:36:38,533
...didn't go to the play?

982
01:36:39,196 --> 01:36:41,413
I went.  - So?

983
01:36:42,118 --> 01:36:45,017
I came from there
for a reason - really?

984
01:36:45,311 --> 01:36:48,013
Are you lying too?
- Yes, I say.

985
01:36:48,840 --> 01:36:50,656
But it doesn't bother anyone...

986
01:36:51,374 --> 01:36:54,073
...only if it's not
something that I gain from.

987
01:36:56,605 --> 01:36:58,853
I have seen the drama
Chandalika several times.

988
01:36:58,933 --> 01:37:03,974
Yes, how is it?
- Don't you know its story?  - No.

989
01:37:05,213 --> 01:37:06,893
Then why didn't you come there?

990
01:37:10,158 --> 01:37:11,274
just

991
01:37:12,052 --> 01:37:15,183
It's a beautiful story.
- Please tell me.

992
01:37:16,955 --> 01:37:20,973
Bishmanand is a good
disciple of Buddha.

993
01:37:22,490 --> 01:37:24,973
One day, while walking in
the sun, he felt very sick.

994
01:37:26,011 --> 01:37:27,473
As he approached a well he saw.

995
01:37:27,992 --> 01:37:29,626
...a girl draws water from it.

996
01:37:29,869 --> 01:37:32,386
Son!  Could you give
me some water, please?

997
01:37:33,104 --> 01:37:37,912
No, sir, I'm sorry.
- Why is that?

998
01:37:38,413 --> 01:37:42,746
I was born in a very low caste.

999
01:37:43,092 --> 01:37:47,002
You have misunderstood
the child, just like us.

1000
01:37:48,230 --> 01:37:50,825
This comforts everyone...

1001
01:37:50,905 --> 01:37:54,469
...everyone's thirty nivana
water belongs to everyone.

1002
01:37:55,175 --> 01:38:00,520
But sir, I belong to the Shudra caste.
- That's a lie.

1003
01:38:02,085 --> 01:38:05,035
Oh beautiful children,
the monsoons bring...

1004
01:38:05,115 --> 01:38:08,086
...Black clouds are also
called Chandal Megha.

1005
01:38:08,122 --> 01:38:11,668
But does the water coming
from those clouds get dirty?

1006
01:38:11,832 --> 01:38:13,926
When Janaki stopped in the forest...

1007
01:38:14,618 --> 01:38:16,434
...Chandal also brings
water for him to bathe.

1008
01:38:17,091 --> 01:38:22,193
If I give you water,
it will be a sin for you.

1009
01:38:23,430 --> 01:38:25,709
How can I commit
that heinous sin?

1010
01:38:25,789 --> 01:38:30,357
No, children, that would
do me a lot of good.

1011
01:38:31,395 --> 01:38:33,469
Don't let yourself down.

1012
01:38:33,504 --> 01:38:36,321
Buddha said if someone
insults himself...

1013
01:38:36,411 --> 01:38:39,029
...that it is a greater
sin than suicide.

1014
01:38:40,519 --> 01:38:45,890
I am very tired children
please give me some water.

1015
01:38:53,019 --> 01:38:57,387
That Chandal girl quenched
Bishmanand's thirst.

1016
01:38:58,408 --> 01:39:00,109
He blessed him.

1017
01:39:01,672 --> 01:39:03,962
Since then, he considered
himself as a human being...

1018
01:39:04,696 --> 01:39:06,952
...not as a low caste person.

1019
01:39:09,983 --> 01:39:12,100
But that was in the old days

1020
01:39:14,203 --> 01:39:15,636
Do such things happen in our time?

1021
01:39:21,469 --> 01:39:24,417
Why Sujata?  Such a great
man was born in our time...

1022
01:39:25,344 --> 01:39:27,060
...for the lower
castes all their lives...

1023
01:39:27,140 --> 01:39:30,263
...someone dedicated to
stopping injustice from happening.

1024
01:39:30,956 --> 01:39:32,204
Mr. Gandhi.

1025
01:39:34,491 --> 01:39:35,657
haven't you heard...

1026
01:39:35,737 --> 01:39:38,169
...the story about the
low caste girl Lakshmi?

1027
01:39:38,731 --> 01:39:42,017
Gandhi treated Lakshmi
as his own daughter...

1028
01:39:42,574 --> 01:39:44,843
...He allowed him to stay
in his Ashram in Ahmedabad.

1029
01:39:45,721 --> 01:39:47,464
Then a big problem arose.

1030
01:39:47,949 --> 01:39:51,581
People stopped supporting
the ashram because of that girl.

1031
01:39:51,663 --> 01:39:54,516
But Gandhi did not
change his mind.

1032
01:39:54,549 --> 01:39:56,328
How can a man
belittle another man...

1033
01:39:56,626 --> 01:39:58,134
...that too based on religion?

1034
01:39:59,089 --> 01:40:02,189
He could not bear the
humiliation of this religion.

1035
01:40:02,612 --> 01:40:05,137
He faced the hatred of
those who supported him...

1036
01:40:05,428 --> 01:40:07,697
...but he did not expel
that girl from the ashram.

1037
01:40:08,015 --> 01:40:11,135
Finally, the ashram came to the point where it had to be closed.

1038
01:40:11,578 --> 01:40:14,421
Next, as if by God's blessing...

1039
01:40:14,501 --> 01:40:17,327
...The ashram received a grant of 13,000 rupees.

1040
01:40:18,054 --> 01:40:20,081
Gandhi's patience paid off.

1041
01:40:22,855 --> 01:40:25,333
why this  why are you crying

1042
01:40:26,916 --> 01:40:28,113
I'm not crying.

1043
01:40:29,795 --> 01:40:31,891
Who can cry when hearing
such a beautiful story?

1044
01:40:42,499 --> 01:40:44,976
Today I feel like everything
here is more beautiful than before.

1045
01:40:46,110 --> 01:40:47,453
Don't you feel the same way?

1046
01:41:00,526 --> 01:41:01,607
Sujata!

1047
01:41:04,367 --> 01:41:06,180
Why do I like you so much?

1048
01:41:08,982 --> 01:41:14,739
Tell me Sujata.
- We're getting late, let's go.

1049
01:41:17,624 --> 01:41:20,052
Why are you trying to run
away without answering me?

1050
01:41:23,234 --> 01:41:26,071
If I know you like
me the same way...

1051
01:41:26,151 --> 01:41:31,530
"Oh Brother"

1052
01:41:33,502 --> 01:41:38,020
"Listen, friend."

1053
01:41:39,293 --> 01:41:43,708
"Ask, my friend."

1054
01:41:53,049 --> 01:41:55,263
Why are you silent?
Won't you answer me?

1055
01:41:59,462 --> 01:42:01,580
do you know?
I saw a dream Sujata

1056
01:42:03,109 --> 01:42:04,203
what a dream

1057
01:42:05,282 --> 01:42:07,565
You had a chandramalika flower in your hair.

1058
01:42:08,617 --> 01:42:10,270
There was a red sandalwood mark on the forehead.

1059
01:42:14,228 --> 01:42:15,888
You were wearing a beautiful saree…

1060
01:42:16,504 --> 01:42:19,182
...You stood beside me
like a beautiful statue.

1061
01:42:21,506 --> 01:42:23,658
Tell me, what could be
the meaning of that dream?

1062
01:42:26,598 --> 01:42:28,674
It means you have
beautiful ideas.

1063
01:42:28,902 --> 01:42:30,459
Sujata, don't skip the question.

1064
01:42:31,151 --> 01:42:33,628
Tell me, like in that dream,
when will you come to me?

1065
01:42:36,644 --> 01:42:37,848
Any day you like.

1066
01:42:38,672 --> 01:42:46,505
At that moment I will be yours...

1067
01:42:46,585 --> 01:42:54,039
In that moment you will be mine...

1068
01:44:08,035 --> 01:44:09,275
Say it out loud.

1069
01:44:10,936 --> 01:44:14,098
Now I only know the tune.
I can't find the right words.

1070
01:44:14,472 --> 01:44:17,974
Tell me directly that you can't
sing, why do you apologize?

1071
01:44:18,035 --> 01:44:21,226
I promise, Sujatha, as soon as I
get the words, I will sing for you.

1072
01:44:55,160 --> 01:44:58,406
Sujata!
- Brother Mahadev?  Come on.

1073
01:45:00,136 --> 01:45:02,398
The husband and wife
have come - and Rama?

1074
01:45:02,571 --> 01:45:04,363
Lady Rama has not come yet.

1075
01:45:14,310 --> 01:45:16,701
Aunt Sujata is looking for someone.

1076
01:45:16,755 --> 01:45:18,720
Now it is not a good thing
to delay this issue any more.

1077
01:45:18,800 --> 01:45:23,305
But he is older than him.
- We don't have time to choose between good and bad.

1078
01:45:24,035 --> 01:45:25,785
Where can we find a
good young man for him?

1079
01:45:26,958 --> 01:45:30,715
I don't like the way Adir
suddenly got up from the drama.

1080
01:45:30,795 --> 01:45:32,035
I don't know what happened.

1081
01:45:32,788 --> 01:45:34,752
Maybe he has
important work to do.

1082
01:45:34,832 --> 01:45:38,080
No, boys are very different these days.

1083
01:45:38,395 --> 01:45:40,320
It is very difficult to
understand their ideas.

1084
01:45:41,135 --> 01:45:45,187
Aunt says Adir is
ready to marry Rama...

1085
01:45:45,995 --> 01:45:48,720
...There is no need to wait
until Rama finishes the exam.

1086
01:45:48,961 --> 01:45:53,368
If Rama can't marry a gem
like Adir, I am very afraid for him.

1087
01:46:42,652 --> 01:46:47,232
hello  - Hello Sujata, I only
remembered the tune at that time.

1088
01:46:47,632 --> 01:46:49,610
Now I found the words, listen.

1089
01:50:56,780 --> 01:51:00,109
are you smiling  Apparently
you don't like my song.

1090
01:51:01,060 --> 01:51:05,143
No, no, I'm not laughing.

1091
01:51:07,513 --> 01:51:10,843
Everything I told you today
on the river bank was a lie.

1092
01:51:12,288 --> 01:51:17,071
Pure lies please
forget all that.

1093
01:51:17,442 --> 01:51:20,400
What are you talking about Sujata?
- Yes.

1094
01:51:21,438 --> 01:51:25,235
If you want to see me happy,
don't tell aunty any of these things.

1095
01:51:25,979 --> 01:51:28,884
Neither he nor my parents want it.

1096
01:51:30,397 --> 01:51:34,816
I'm asking you, don't
ask me about it again.

1097
01:51:35,848 --> 01:51:38,076
Sujata!  Sujata!

1098
01:52:08,561 --> 01:52:09,754
Listen, Sujata...

1099
01:52:20,195 --> 01:52:25,218
Monara Ragum Devi;
His eyes are open.

1100
01:52:25,918 --> 01:52:28,547
See the sky absorbed in thought.

1101
01:52:29,135 --> 01:52:33,364
Today my dreams have come true.

1102
01:52:33,909 --> 01:52:36,685
We have joined.

1103
01:52:37,074 --> 01:52:40,490
The music of this rain...
How are you sister?

1104
01:52:40,663 --> 01:52:44,157
do you eat tamarind  - No.
- Eat them, they are very tasty.

1105
01:52:45,653 --> 01:52:49,891
Rama!  Why does Mr. Adir
praise you so much?

1106
01:52:50,497 --> 01:52:53,800
who  Mr. Adir, are you praising me?

1107
01:52:54,968 --> 01:52:59,301
In any case, you are going to praise
me, why is there something to ask?

1108
01:53:00,434 --> 01:53:04,050
But... Why is Mr. Adir
especially praised?

1109
01:53:07,388 --> 01:53:11,504
Even the cook who
makes the roti praises me.

1110
01:53:14,548 --> 01:53:16,901
No Rama, this is no joke.

1111
01:53:17,601 --> 01:53:22,896
Please think.
- What are you trying to say?

1112
01:53:24,806 --> 01:53:27,582
Good people like Mr. Adir
are very few in this world.

1113
01:53:28,041 --> 01:53:29,375
There is no doubt about it.

1114
01:53:33,100 --> 01:53:35,418
I'm afraid he will be sad.

1115
01:53:35,877 --> 01:53:39,077
What should I do if he
has inherited sadness?

1116
01:53:39,259 --> 01:53:42,425
Sister, I can't speak any more names.
I'm leaving.

1117
01:54:00,362 --> 01:54:02,419
I brought tea, father.
- Where is mom?

1118
01:54:02,636 --> 01:54:03,762
It's coming too.

1119
01:54:04,815 --> 01:54:06,830
why this  why are you sad

1120
01:54:07,107 --> 01:54:10,756
There's nothing wrong with you, right?
- Nothing like that, dad, I'm fine.

1121
01:54:16,562 --> 01:54:17,856
Aunt just spoke.

1122
01:54:18,072 --> 01:54:21,480
He has decided Sujata's marriage.
- Did he do that?

1123
01:54:22,699 --> 01:54:24,325
At least we didn't see that kiss.

1124
01:54:24,930 --> 01:54:26,625
Don't go creating problems now.

1125
01:54:27,022 --> 01:54:29,503
If Sujata doesn't get married soon...

1126
01:54:29,928 --> 01:54:32,162
...We will also have to postpone
the marriage of Rama and Adir.

1127
01:54:34,373 --> 01:54:35,792
The girls of this time.

1128
01:54:36,164 --> 01:54:39,362
You never know when
they will change their mind.

1129
01:54:39,805 --> 01:54:43,619
If we lose someone so good, I
will not be able to bear my grief.

1130
01:55:16,094 --> 01:55:18,472
I came to talk to you and
make a decision.  If you think...

1131
01:55:18,552 --> 01:55:22,857
Don't make the same mistake
again, I can't marry you.

1132
01:55:23,765 --> 01:55:25,045
why not

1133
01:55:27,414 --> 01:55:29,014
Because it will be a big loss for you.

1134
01:55:30,071 --> 01:55:32,622
I am smart enough to think
about my profit and loss.

1135
01:55:33,469 --> 01:55:35,666
Then why are you
doing such a stupid thing?

1136
01:55:37,197 --> 01:55:39,826
You can find a
better wife than me.

1137
01:55:40,354 --> 01:55:42,814
No, I can't find one.

1138
01:55:46,528 --> 01:55:50,734
You belong to an important family.
You belong to a high caste.

1139
01:55:51,959 --> 01:55:54,494
You know that, right?
- Yes, I know.

1140
01:55:55,738 --> 01:55:57,373
Then you know
your lower caste...

1141
01:55:57,909 --> 01:56:01,377
...that there are many people in castes.
- Yes.

1142
01:56:02,043 --> 01:56:04,188
The thoughts of low people are also very low.

1143
01:56:04,707 --> 01:56:06,134
What happened to you Sujata?

1144
01:56:06,740 --> 01:56:08,322
Why are you reading
nonsense today?

1145
01:56:10,363 --> 01:56:12,214
There is a reason for that.
- what?

1146
01:56:15,534 --> 01:56:17,094
I do not belong to your caste.

1147
01:56:19,505 --> 01:56:23,574
Are you trying to say that
you are not related to Mr. Upen?

1148
01:56:25,828 --> 01:56:28,700
There is a blood relation with it...

1149
01:56:29,003 --> 01:56:31,251
...I don't even
belong to his club.

1150
01:56:32,686 --> 01:56:38,974
I belong to a very low caste,
I belong to the lowest caste.

1151
01:56:50,951 --> 01:56:54,013
So?  why don't you talk

1152
01:56:56,253 --> 01:56:58,051
Will you come back to find me?

1153
01:56:59,021 --> 01:57:01,762
Do you want to marry me now?

1154
01:57:13,544 --> 01:57:16,853
Are you trying to scare me, Sujata?
It can't be!

1155
01:57:17,813 --> 01:57:19,424
I don't like that caste discrimination.

1156
01:57:22,224 --> 01:57:25,423
Whoever you are, you are my dream.

1157
01:57:25,692 --> 01:57:28,824
You taught me love, you taught me...

1158
01:57:28,904 --> 01:57:33,624
That's Mr. Adir!
In the name of God, say nothing more.

1159
01:57:34,757 --> 01:57:36,144
I can't stand it.

1160
01:57:40,585 --> 01:57:44,590
You still can't marry me.
- Why is that?

1161
01:57:45,629 --> 01:57:47,999
For what reason do you
say no to my love again?

1162
01:57:49,140 --> 01:57:53,041
Is there any secret?
- Yes, there is such a secret.

1163
01:57:53,300 --> 01:57:55,824
what?  - Please don't ask that

1164
01:57:56,882 --> 01:58:01,904
I'm telling you, don't listen again,
I can't stand listening to them.

1165
01:58:04,224 --> 01:58:06,533
Forget about a low
caste girl like me.

1166
01:58:07,519 --> 01:58:11,824
Imagine that the girl
of your dreams died.

1167
01:58:13,269 --> 01:58:16,790
Chandramalika flower is lost.

1168
01:58:35,524 --> 01:58:38,731
Why are you sitting in the dark, son?
- Just.

1169
01:58:40,011 --> 01:58:42,684
You said you can't even go out.

1170
01:58:42,891 --> 01:58:46,446
So where did you just go?
- To Rama's house.

1171
01:58:47,864 --> 01:58:53,227
If so, then you must have received the news.
-what?

1172
01:58:53,538 --> 01:58:57,758
That low caste girl in
their house... Sujata...

1173
01:58:58,528 --> 01:59:00,113
...his marriage decision.

1174
01:59:00,690 --> 01:59:04,885
The boy is poor in his caste but rich.

1175
01:59:05,637 --> 01:59:08,007
Sujath is very happy about it.

1176
01:59:09,667 --> 01:59:14,338
Okay, so you can
rest a bit, I'll hit God.

