02:00:23,649 --> 02:00:26,209
hello  - Hello Rama,
I'm talking to Adir.

1178
02:00:26,806 --> 02:00:28,769
Sujata wants to talk.
- Hold on.

1179
02:00:40,877 --> 02:00:44,803
hello  - Who is Sujata?
best wishes.

1180
02:00:45,633 --> 02:00:49,432
I heard that you are going
to marry a very rich man.

1181
02:00:49,438 --> 02:00:52,993
In the end, you rejected
my love because of money.

1182
02:00:53,011 --> 02:00:55,789
You know who would give
up everything for money?

1183
02:00:56,002 --> 02:00:57,948
Today I had to believe...

1184
02:00:58,321 --> 02:01:01,789
...that low caste people
only have low thoughts.

1185
02:01:02,118 --> 02:01:04,521
You are the best example of that.

1186
02:01:05,395 --> 02:01:07,323
What are you talking
about, Mr. Adir?

1187
02:01:08,361 --> 02:01:10,696
Who messaged you
about my marriage?

1188
02:01:10,886 --> 02:01:12,503
Someone I can trust.

1189
02:01:16,932 --> 02:01:21,447
Then come to my wedding.
- Why is that?

1190
02:01:23,626 --> 02:01:28,019
This low caste girl
rubs on your feet...

1191
02:01:28,737 --> 02:01:35,124
... He will shave his
hair and leave the world.

1192
02:01:36,287 --> 02:01:39,149
Sujata!  Listen Sujata!

1193
02:01:39,832 --> 02:01:43,690
Sujata!  Listen Sujata!

1194
02:01:44,390 --> 02:01:47,253
Sujata!

1195
02:02:08,139 --> 02:02:10,215
Grandma!  - Yes, son?

1196
02:02:11,175 --> 02:02:13,580
Do you want me
to get married soon?

1197
02:02:15,439 --> 02:02:19,755
What a stupid question, boy!
That's what I live for.

1198
02:02:20,308 --> 02:02:22,364
When will a beautiful
daughter-in-law come to this house?

1199
02:02:22,434 --> 02:02:24,236
So prepare the
necessary things now.

1200
02:02:24,321 --> 02:02:27,029
I want to get Dighayu!

1201
02:02:27,109 --> 02:02:29,390
I will send a
message to Upen soon

1202
02:02:29,978 --> 02:02:31,993
But Rama's exams...

1203
02:02:32,073 --> 02:02:34,631
I want to marry Sujata, not Rama.

1204
02:02:34,850 --> 02:02:36,574
what  what did you say

1205
02:02:36,940 --> 02:02:38,851
I want to marry Sujatha.

1206
02:02:42,371 --> 02:02:45,596
Do you know that she is not Upen's daughter?
- Yes.

1207
02:02:46,816 --> 02:02:49,403
And you know he is low caste?
- Yes, I know.

1208
02:02:49,483 --> 02:02:51,330
God is the witness!

1209
02:02:53,944 --> 02:02:58,562
Are you going to marry that
low caste girl in front of my god?

1210
02:02:58,744 --> 02:03:00,698
Go out of my sight, go!

1211
02:03:01,312 --> 02:03:04,953
Is it not your God
who created Sujatawa?

1212
02:03:07,755 --> 02:03:11,604
Like Buddha,
Ramakrishna, Vivekananda...

1213
02:03:12,157 --> 02:03:13,973
...the people you hang around here...

1214
02:03:14,198 --> 02:03:17,170
...never said about caste
differences among people.

1215
02:03:17,380 --> 02:03:20,891
Don't read nonsense!
They are important scholars.

1216
02:03:21,323 --> 02:03:23,111
They are great...

1217
02:03:23,125 --> 02:03:25,570
...for thinking that
everyone is human.

1218
02:03:25,716 --> 02:03:27,861
It is a great sin to hate another
human being, grandmother.

1219
02:03:27,941 --> 02:03:29,170
Keep your advice to yourself!

1220
02:03:29,357 --> 02:03:30,770
Come to teach me about religion!

1221
02:03:31,060 --> 02:03:34,277
Listen well!  You
can't marry that girl.

1222
02:03:34,331 --> 02:03:36,419
She is a child of low caste parents.

1223
02:03:36,500 --> 02:03:40,250
I don't believe it, now
she is Mr. Upen's daughter.

1224
02:03:40,435 --> 02:03:41,770
You mean then she...

1225
02:03:41,850 --> 02:03:44,127
Does being born into the
lower castes change them?

1226
02:03:44,551 --> 02:03:46,004
Now then the problem is in the genes?

1227
02:03:46,367 --> 02:03:49,204
Then if a Brahmin child
was adopted by a Shudra...

1228
02:03:49,490 --> 02:03:50,917
...and still you think
he is a brahmin?

1229
02:03:50,997 --> 02:03:54,557
No, then his caste will disappear
and then he will be a Shudra.

1230
02:03:54,560 --> 02:03:55,863
So I can say...

1231
02:03:55,943 --> 02:03:57,870
...Now Sujata is also
the daughter of a Brahmin

1232
02:03:57,904 --> 02:04:00,507
Because he was brought up by
an important person like Mr. Upen.

1233
02:04:01,190 --> 02:04:04,901
A man becomes high and low
according to the way he is raised.

1234
02:04:04,981 --> 02:04:07,617
Shut up!  You can't beat
me with those arguments.

1235
02:04:08,084 --> 02:04:11,490
This is my final decision,
you cannot marry that girl.

1236
02:04:12,261 --> 02:04:13,850
So my final decision is...

1237
02:04:14,354 --> 02:04:16,551
...I will not marry
anyone except Sujatha.

1238
02:04:17,018 --> 02:04:19,170
From today you and
I have no relation.

1239
02:04:19,250 --> 02:04:20,490
Run away from my house!

1240
02:04:22,156 --> 02:04:24,793
You have no right to
my property or money.

1241
02:04:37,766 --> 02:04:42,946
my goodness!  Why are you giving
me so much trouble at this old age?

1242
02:04:49,500 --> 02:04:51,784
Lady!  The husband is about to leave

1243
02:04:52,848 --> 02:04:54,316
Lady!

1244
02:04:57,068 --> 02:04:58,824
The husband is really going to leave.

1245
02:04:59,750 --> 02:05:01,099
Please hurry lady!

1246
02:05:05,554 --> 02:05:09,238
Adir, where are you going, Adir?

1247
02:05:09,956 --> 02:05:15,846
Wait, are you really going?
- Yes.

1248
02:05:17,126 --> 02:05:19,592
Are you dishonoring your family?

1249
02:05:20,223 --> 02:05:23,189
...because of the desire of
a low caste who is nowhere?

1250
02:05:24,399 --> 02:05:26,397
I don't believe in that caste system.

1251
02:05:26,907 --> 02:05:29,951
Is your faith the only
thing worth to you now?

1252
02:05:30,790 --> 02:05:32,191
Is your duty irrelevant now?

1253
02:05:33,151 --> 02:05:35,631
You are leaving this
house for a small reason.

1254
02:05:35,711 --> 02:05:42,622
Adir, your mother died
when you were a small boy.

1255
02:05:43,685 --> 02:05:48,431
Since then I raised you.

1256
02:05:50,242 --> 02:05:55,751
I lived because of you.
I forgot about death.

1257
02:05:57,006 --> 02:05:58,182
But you...

1258
02:05:59,047 --> 02:06:04,351
Don't you think
about me even once?

1259
02:06:06,702 --> 02:06:12,618
Don't you think I
have no one but you?

1260
02:06:14,667 --> 02:06:23,047
You're Gyothin, I won't
be able to stay a second.

1261
02:06:27,060 --> 02:06:31,688
I accept defeat, please
don't go, children.

1262
02:06:32,976 --> 02:06:34,715
I open my hands.

1263
02:06:50,353 --> 02:06:51,633
Mr. Adir!

1264
02:06:54,816 --> 02:06:58,890
This letter has arrived, sir.
- from whom?  - From Sujata.

1265
02:07:02,358 --> 02:07:03,646
you can go

1266
02:07:18,779 --> 02:07:21,379
"Mr. Adir, I am
writing you this letter..."

1267
02:07:21,459 --> 02:07:24,334
"...because I can't say
everything over the phone."

1268
02:07:25,155 --> 02:07:30,760
"It was lucky for me that someone
like you loved a low caste like me."

1269
02:07:31,615 --> 02:07:36,683
"But to make you happy I
have to hurt mom and dad."

1270
02:07:37,851 --> 02:07:40,619
"I wouldn't do that for
anything in the world."

1271
02:07:41,648 --> 02:07:44,709
"They want you to bind Rama."

1272
02:07:45,617 --> 02:07:49,499
"If you want to see me
happy, please marry him."

1273
02:07:49,741 --> 02:07:53,909
"I've been with my mom and
dad all my life and I respect them."

1274
02:07:54,177 --> 02:07:55,336
"Of course."

1275
02:08:02,350 --> 02:08:04,772
Charu!  Born!
- Aunt?  Why this time?

1276
02:08:11,950 --> 02:08:15,988
No problem?
- No, nothing like that.

1277
02:08:16,429 --> 02:08:21,532
what's the problem  You look tired.
- Yes, I'm tired.

1278
02:08:26,254 --> 02:08:28,390
I am very tired Charu.

1279
02:08:30,491 --> 02:08:35,614
I came to tell you that Adir
wants to get married soon.

1280
02:08:36,495 --> 02:08:39,194
Really, that's good news.

1281
02:08:39,548 --> 02:08:41,823
But Rama's exams are approaching.

1282
02:08:44,003 --> 02:08:50,801
It is Sujathawa that Adir wants to marry, not Rama.
- Sujatava?!

1283
02:08:51,917 --> 02:08:56,854
Doesn't Adir know that Sujata is from low caste?
- He knows.

1284
02:08:58,254 --> 02:08:59,604
He knows everything.

1285
02:08:59,985 --> 02:09:03,534
But why did you allow this injustice?

1286
02:09:04,058 --> 02:09:07,534
I lost, son.

1287
02:09:07,941 --> 02:09:10,086
I had no answer
to Adir's arguments.

1288
02:09:11,668 --> 02:09:15,774
He grew up in this
new world, he learned.

1289
02:09:16,641 --> 02:09:18,534
Maybe he's right.

1290
02:09:19,945 --> 02:09:23,334
Times are changing
Charu, we can't stop it

1291
02:09:24,511 --> 02:09:28,694
But I also cannot change
my thoughts at this age.

1292
02:09:29,684 --> 02:09:34,277
It would be good if I also go to
Kashi and calm myself down a bit.

1293
02:09:36,854 --> 02:09:38,982
Born here.  - What is this aunt?

1294
02:09:39,578 --> 02:09:41,688
These are fifty thousand
rupees worth of bank shares.

1295
02:09:43,107 --> 02:09:46,834
I thought I would give
these to Adir's wife.

1296
02:09:47,915 --> 02:09:51,677
Anyway, I'll leave these
with you to give to Sujata.

1297
02:09:52,707 --> 02:09:57,854
Now it's better to give up
completely on being a loser anyway.

1298
02:10:16,828 --> 02:10:20,141
After everything, why Adir...
- It's not Adir's fault.

1299
02:10:20,530 --> 02:10:22,398
This is the bad girl's fault.

1300
02:10:22,478 --> 02:10:27,448
Is this how she treats our love?

1301
02:10:27,528 --> 02:10:29,385
Why are you angry Charu?
Someone hears.

1302
02:10:29,465 --> 02:10:31,107
She is like a daughter to us.

1303
02:10:31,383 --> 02:10:33,831
Not like a daughter,
she is a poisonous snake!

1304
02:10:34,237 --> 02:10:34,973
Charu!

1305
02:10:35,053 --> 02:10:37,497
I can't see her
dressed like a bride.

1306
02:10:37,577 --> 02:10:39,185
I can't marry a witch...

1307
02:10:39,265 --> 02:10:40,857
...of someone who took away my daughter's rights.

1308
02:10:40,937 --> 02:10:43,691
Shut up Charu!
- Why do I shut up?

1309
02:10:44,590 --> 02:10:47,479
We have created a snake.

1310
02:10:48,214 --> 02:10:50,741
We petted her, but she bit us.
- Charu!

1311
02:10:50,821 --> 02:10:54,179
What happened mom?
- Shut up!  I'm not your mother.

1312
02:10:54,259 --> 02:10:58,593
Get out of here!
I don't want to see your face again.

1313
02:10:58,673 --> 02:11:01,585
Charu!  - Mom!

1314
02:11:01,665 --> 02:11:03,600
Charu!  - Mom!

1315
02:11:04,025 --> 02:11:04,795
mother

1316
02:11:04,875 --> 02:11:08,228
Charu!  - What happened to mom?
- Lady!

1317
02:11:08,514 --> 02:11:10,659
Come on, let's take him to the room.

1318
02:11:24,078 --> 02:11:26,944
Look Mr. Upen, he
has a lot of blood...

1319
02:11:27,454 --> 02:11:29,918
...His heart rate is decreasing.

1320
02:11:30,491 --> 02:11:34,816
I think he has a concussion
and we have to be careful.

1321
02:11:35,058 --> 02:11:38,181
Do not let him feel too
much anger or happiness.

1322
02:11:38,414 --> 02:11:40,918
And... come this way.

1323
02:11:41,320 --> 02:11:43,785
Nurse!  Check your pulse regularly.
-Okay sir.

1324
02:11:52,537 --> 02:11:56,331
Listen, Mr. Upen, I want to tell you
clearly the condition of the patient...

1325
02:11:56,430 --> 02:11:58,178
...is a bit serious.

1326
02:11:58,258 --> 02:11:59,795
He needs new blood soon.

1327
02:11:59,875 --> 02:12:02,346
I'm ready, take my blood.  - No.

1328
02:12:02,822 --> 02:12:05,304
First we need to see
what his blood type is.

1329
02:12:05,667 --> 02:12:07,206
Next, matching his blood...

1330
02:12:07,286 --> 02:12:09,358
...He wants to take blood
from someone who has blood.

1331
02:12:09,740 --> 02:12:12,214
Ask the laboratory inspector
to come immediately.

1332
02:12:12,586 --> 02:12:17,178
Doctor!  The patient cannot breathe.
- I am coming.

1333
02:12:17,567 --> 02:12:19,558
Listen, don't waste a second.

1334
02:12:21,113 --> 02:12:23,302
I will do it, stay with him.

1335
02:12:35,763 --> 02:12:38,171
No, his blood is not compatible.

1336
02:12:38,896 --> 02:12:41,231
Doctor, the patient's
pulse is gone.

1337
02:12:41,421 --> 02:12:43,393
Prepare a choramine injection.

1338
02:12:47,682 --> 02:12:49,827
What do we do now?
- I don't understand.

1339
02:12:50,251 --> 02:12:51,609
We need to find blood soon.

1340
02:12:52,699 --> 02:12:56,132
Is there no one else here?
- Please, look at my blood.

1341
02:12:58,822 --> 02:13:01,736
Sujata, you...
- Yes, father

1342
02:13:02,142 --> 02:13:05,713
Come, sit here.
Sahani, look at the blood...

1343
02:13:05,793 --> 02:13:07,523
...I will give the injection
to the patient until then.

1344
02:13:35,994 --> 02:13:37,371
So doctor?

1345
02:13:40,787 --> 02:13:42,957
His blood matches the
patient's blood exactly.

1346
02:13:43,269 --> 02:13:44,808
Same type.  - Thank God!

1347
02:13:45,275 --> 02:13:47,532
Come on, let's not waste time.

1348
02:13:47,722 --> 02:13:48,846
Come on, Dr. Sahani.

1349
02:15:10,872 --> 02:15:14,272
He is fine now, let him rest.

1350
02:15:15,283 --> 02:15:18,691
Call me at noon and tell me about his condition.

1351
02:15:19,305 --> 02:15:20,412
Nurse!

1352
02:15:28,258 --> 02:15:32,177
You've been up all night.  Go and rest.
- Okay.

1353
02:15:42,590 --> 02:15:45,497
Hello, hello doctor, I
am talking to Rama.

1354
02:15:45,687 --> 02:15:47,780
You said to inform
about mother's condition.

1355
02:15:49,976 --> 02:15:52,364
Mom has no problem
now, she is sleeping now.

1356
02:15:53,402 --> 02:15:57,052
OK, I'll tell dad then
I'll leave it, doctor.

1357
02:16:02,353 --> 02:16:05,078
Last night I was
troubled by this question.

1358
02:16:05,312 --> 02:16:09,496
what is that  - How did Sujata's
blood match Charu's blood...

1359
02:16:09,576 --> 02:16:11,298
You think even blood...

1360
02:16:11,765 --> 02:16:15,922
...like people are
divided into high and low?

1361
02:16:16,885 --> 02:16:18,666
What are you guys talking about?

1362
02:16:20,509 --> 02:16:23,639
He is fine now.
I will go home for a while.

1363
02:16:29,002 --> 02:16:30,402
What was Adir saying?

1364
02:16:30,482 --> 02:16:34,028
Charu defeated Sujata.
- Who?  - All of us.

1365
02:16:34,511 --> 02:16:36,223
You wanted fresh blood.

1366
02:16:36,577 --> 02:16:40,482
Neither mine nor Adir's nor
Rama's blood was compatible.

1367
02:16:40,876 --> 02:16:43,202
But Sujata's blood...
- What are you talking about?

1368
02:16:45,002 --> 02:16:47,294
Did Sujata save me by giving her blood?

1369
02:16:47,374 --> 02:16:49,145
Don't get up... lie down.

1370
02:16:50,684 --> 02:16:57,118
But...how did his
blood match mine?

1371
02:16:57,198 --> 02:17:01,053
Don't ask me that, sir.
Only God can answer that.

1372
02:17:01,961 --> 02:17:06,042
He is the one who made me,
made you and made Sujatawa.

1373
02:17:06,347 --> 02:17:08,722
Maybe he treated
everyone the same.

1374
02:17:10,056 --> 02:17:13,100
We lost very badly, Charu.

1375
02:17:13,775 --> 02:17:17,027
After Sujata saved you
by giving her blood...

1376
02:17:17,355 --> 02:17:19,708
...Now he doesn't owe us anything

1377
02:17:20,434 --> 02:17:22,960
He paid us back for
everything we did to him.

1378
02:17:25,432 --> 02:17:30,673
It's true, now we have no
reason to be angry with it.

1379
02:17:32,128 --> 02:17:36,038
where is he  - In that room,
the doctor told him to rest.

1380
02:17:36,824 --> 02:17:38,041
Shall I call him?

1381
02:17:40,050 --> 02:17:41,494
No, not now.

1382
02:17:48,189 --> 02:17:49,417
Sujata!

1383
02:17:56,620 --> 02:18:00,504
Was what you wrote in your letter true?

1384
02:18:02,140 --> 02:18:06,413
Won't your decision change?
- No.

1385
02:18:08,056 --> 02:18:10,192
It's a shame you sent your aunt here.

1386
02:18:12,657 --> 02:18:15,987
I can't marry you.  - why?

1387
02:18:18,599 --> 02:18:20,969
It was because of me that mother faced this trouble.

1388
02:18:22,223 --> 02:18:27,057
didn't you hear
My breath is poison.

1389
02:18:30,196 --> 02:18:34,555
Please go to save
yourself from that poison.

1390
02:18:49,507 --> 02:18:51,030
Are you saying goodbye to me with those words?

1391
02:18:52,526 --> 02:18:57,093
Say nothing else?
- I want to say.

1392
02:18:58,926 --> 02:19:03,933
Then tell Sujata.
- Before you go, promise me something.

1393
02:19:05,022 --> 02:19:10,626
That you forget me and hate me.

1394
02:19:13,197 --> 02:19:18,706
I'm leaving, but I don't
think I can hate you.

1395
02:19:19,839 --> 02:19:21,940
There is no room for hate in my love.

1396
02:19:24,119 --> 02:19:27,527
Sujata, you made a
mistake by loving me.

1397
02:19:27,717 --> 02:19:33,583
Yes, I was stupid
and I made a mistake.

1398
02:19:34,592 --> 02:19:37,665
That mistake of yours
now helps me survive.

1399
02:19:39,316 --> 02:19:43,657
I have no other way,
I have no other refuge.

1400
02:19:45,431 --> 02:19:49,496
Agree to what I
say and marry Rama.

1401
02:19:50,188 --> 02:19:51,805
You will be happy.

1402
02:19:52,324 --> 02:19:54,823
Don't insult me ​​with
such things, Sujata.

1403
02:19:56,362 --> 02:19:58,239
I cannot deceive Rama.

1404
02:19:59,641 --> 02:20:02,062
It is not a problem to be
deceived like this and bear it.

1405
02:20:04,830 --> 02:20:06,948
I will never see you again.

1406
02:20:18,373 --> 02:20:22,991
Here is your letter, what is
the use of this for me now?

1407
02:20:27,012 --> 02:20:32,781
Please forgive me, tell me
you forgive me before you go.

1408
02:20:34,302 --> 02:20:37,044
I can't spoil mommy
and daddy's happiness.

1409
02:20:37,805 --> 02:20:39,612
I can't hurt them.

1410
02:21:02,989 --> 02:21:05,842
Charu, Sujata has failed us once again.

1411
02:21:06,128 --> 02:21:09,102
He uprooted our mane first.

1412
02:21:09,448 --> 02:21:11,057
Here, read this letter.

1413
02:21:14,425 --> 02:21:21,427
"But to make you happy I
have to hurt mom and dad."

1414
02:21:22,300 --> 02:21:25,561
"I wouldn't do it for
anything in the world."

1415
02:21:29,877 --> 02:21:31,312
We are defeated sir.

1416
02:21:31,519 --> 02:21:34,097
But I feel happy
about our defeat today.

1417
02:21:35,653 --> 02:21:38,040
Tell me really
Charu this is really...

1418
02:21:38,120 --> 02:21:42,624
...are the words of Sujata whom
we thought was our daughter?

1419
02:21:43,462 --> 02:21:45,953
He is even better...

1420
02:21:46,601 --> 02:21:51,145
Today I understand
how much Sujata loves us.

1421
02:21:52,881 --> 02:21:54,825
He showed us our mistakes.

1422
02:21:56,220 --> 02:22:00,560
Talk to him, please, talk to him.
- Dad!

1423
02:22:02,688 --> 02:22:03,941
Dad!

1424
02:22:12,823 --> 02:22:13,870
I brought you tea.

1425
02:22:13,950 --> 02:22:17,165
Why talk out loud?  Get in.

1426
02:22:18,107 --> 02:22:23,928
No, I'm not letting my
bad shadow fall on mom.

1427
02:22:24,464 --> 02:22:28,719
Talk... talk to him.
- Come Sujata.

1428
02:22:37,575 --> 02:22:40,455
why are you standing
Leave it and sit down.

1429
02:22:48,931 --> 02:22:53,246
Not there, Sujata is right
here on the other side of me.

1430
02:23:03,504 --> 02:23:07,145
did you hear  Adir
wants to marry you.

1431
02:23:08,787 --> 02:23:11,771
No, mom, no.  - why?

1432
02:23:13,224 --> 02:23:17,305
I will never marry, I
will always be with you.

1433
02:23:18,361 --> 02:23:24,735
Every girl gets married Sujata.
- No, marry Rama.

1434
02:23:26,015 --> 02:23:30,339
Rama is married, but you
should be married too, Sujata.

1435
02:23:32,449 --> 02:23:36,237
You're like our...
- Mom!  Don't say that!

1436
02:23:36,921 --> 02:23:39,290
Don't say that, mom.
- Listen...

1437
02:23:40,173 --> 02:23:46,573
Like a daughter to us!
I can't take it mom, I can't.

1438
02:23:46,653 --> 02:23:48,225
You are not like our daughter.

1439
02:23:49,151 --> 02:23:53,354
You are our daughter, yes our daughter.

1440
02:23:54,468 --> 02:23:59,746
what did you say
Please say that again.

1441
02:23:59,826 --> 02:24:02,901
Yes, you are our daughter.

1442
02:24:05,219 --> 02:24:09,329
Mom!  Mom!  - Son!

1443
02:24:09,409 --> 02:24:15,612
Say that again mom!  I
couldn't wait to hear it.

1444
02:24:17,085 --> 02:24:20,718
Mom!  Mom!

1445
02:24:22,711 --> 02:24:25,838
Hey why is this?  what's the problem

1446
02:24:26,655 --> 02:24:28,095
Why are you all crying?

1447
02:24:28,434 --> 02:24:31,225
We are not crying,
Sujata is crying.

1448
02:24:31,644 --> 02:24:33,900
why are you crying sister

1449
02:24:34,834 --> 02:24:36,750
